sentences: Griffiths with fellow Craigie Senior High School classmate Shahbaz Rind (Dyna-mikes ) founded Downsyde in 1996.
It was the following year that they released a demo cassette Behind the Bucket which topped the independent charts within a week of its release.

In 2000 they released their debut album, Epinonimous, this was followed by Land of the Giants in 2003 and When the Dust Settles in 2005.

Optamus released his debut solo album Forever & A Day on 12 June 2010.
Optamus released his debut solo album Forever & A Day on 12 June 2010.
Optamus previewed the album to a sold out home crowd (Rosemount Hotel W. A) and a huge tour through the southwest in June 2010. '
Forever and A Day' went on to sell 3500 copies from the optamus.com.au website without any distro or label support.
Optamus has indicated that he will be releasing a second album in 2019, to be titled A Hero's Concerto.
A Hero's Concerto was released on September 20, 2019.
